<div class="mb-6">
  <%= link_to "← Back to Items", items_path, class: "inline-block bg-primary text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-dark transition-all duration-200 shadow-md text-lg font-semibold" %>
</div>


<div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-12 max-w-4xl">
  <%# Page Header %>
  <div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">How to Browse & Rent Items</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">A step-by-step guide for Teachers & TAs on renting and listing items.</p>
  </div>

  <%# Section: Browsing Items %>
  <div class="mt-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary">🔍 Browsing Available Items</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2">
      You can search for items using the <span class="font-medium">Search Bar</span> at the top of the Items Page.
      Apply filters to narrow your search.
    </p>
    
    <%# Styled Info Box %>
    <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 mt-4 rounded-lg shadow-md">
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        📌 Tip: Click on an item to see its details and information.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# Section: Renting Items %>
  <div class="mt-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary">🛒 Renting an Item (For Teachers & TAs Only)</h2>
    
    <%# Eligibility %>
    <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 mt-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-primary">
      <p class="font-semibold">✅ Who can rent out items?</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700">
        <li>Teachers</li>
        <li>Teaching Assistants (TAs)</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p class="font-semibold mt-2">❌ Who cannot rent out items?</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">Students must have TA's or admins rent the items out. They cannot do it themselves.</p>
    </div>

    <%# Steps to Rent %>
    <div class="mt-6">
      <p class="text-gray-700">Follow these steps:</p>
      <ul class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 mt-2 space-y-2">
        <li>Click "Rent Now" on an item.</li>
        <li>Confirm your pickup details and submit.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <%# Approval Process %>
    <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 mt-4 rounded-lg shadow-md">
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        ⏳ Some items require may require extra approval. You’ll receive a confirmation email when approved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# Section: Returning Items %>
  <div class="mt-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary">🔄 Returning Items</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2">
      Ensure the item is returned on time. Once done, mark it as returned in the system.
      If you encounter any issues, report them immediately.
      If a student returns a damaged items. You may add a comment to each renting about how the item is damaged by clicking on the add comment button.
    </p>
  </div>

  <%# Section: Listing Items %>
  <div class="mt-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary">📤 Listing an Item for Rent</h2>
    
    <%# Who Can List Items? %>
    <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 mt-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-primary">
      <p class="font-semibold">✅ Who can list items?</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">Only Teachers and TAs can list items.</p>
      
      <p class="font-semibold mt-2">❌ Who cannot list items?</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">Students cannot list items.</p>
    </div>

    <%# Steps to List Items %>
    <div class="mt-6">
      <p class="text-gray-700">Follow these steps:</p>
      <ul class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 mt-2 space-y-2">
        <li>Go to the "Add New Item" page.</li>
        <li>Enter all required information.</li>
        <li>Click Create Item.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <%# Managing Rental Requests %>
    <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 mt-4 rounded-lg shadow-md">
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        📩 You will see all rentings in the rentings table. Only TA's and Admins are able to view this table. 
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# Section: Policies %>
  <div class="mt-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary">⚠️ Important Rules & Policies</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2">
      - Only Teachers and TAs can rent or list items.<br>
      - Damaged Items: Any damage must be reported immediately.
    </p>
  </div>

  <%# Contact Support %>
  <div class="mt-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary">💬 Need More Help?</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2">
      If you have any questions, <a href="mailto:james.reyes@tamu.edu" class="text-primary font-medium">contact support</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
